data.description: Beautiful low-maintenance living in desirable Hayden Hill in the heart of Hardin Valley. This 3 bedroom 3 bathroom home has been meticulously maintained and is ready for you. The property features a primary bedroom, second bedroom and office on the main level. The second floor features large bonus room and third bedroom. Also, all stainless appliances, fenced-in backyard, gas heat and a covered patio. Schedule your showing today!
